
Loops:-->
	Looping is a programming feature with facilitates the
	execution of set of iteration to evaluate particular condition.
	
	
	Advantages of loops:-->
		
			=> We can reduce lines of code..
			=> We can iterate set of data to evaluate any single condition
			
			
	Loops available in java:-->
	
			=> For
			=> while
			=> Do-while
			=> for-each
			
			
			
			
			
			
			
			
			
			
			
			
			
			
			
			
			
			
			
			
	